#: ../../../changelog.md:105
msgid ""
"This version adds multi-environment support with instance-based parameters, "
"allowing multiple independent simulation environments to run simultaneously."
" It also introduces 1D ToF sensor support and keyboard improvements."
msgstr "此版本新增了基于实例参数的多环境支持，允许多个独立的仿真环境同时运行。还引入了 1D ToF 传感器支持和键盘改进。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:108
msgid ""
