#: ../../../changelog.md:149
msgid ""
"This version add the feature of `group_behavior` to support group-level "
"behavior for all objects within the same group, which is more efficient for "
"coordinated behaviors (like swarm or crowd simulation) as it computes "
"actions for all members in a single step. The chinese (中文) version "
"documentation is also supported."
msgstr ""
"此版本添加了 `group_behavior` "
"功能，支持同一组内所有对象的群体级行为，这对于协调行为（如群体或人群仿真）更加高效，因为它可以在单步中计算所有成员的动作。同时支持中文版文档。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:152
msgid ""
"Add `group_behavior` YAML parameter to support group-level behavior for all "
"objects within the same group."
msgstr "新增 `group_behavior` YAML 参数，支持对同组所有物体的组级行为。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:153
msgid ""
"Integrate `GroupBehavior` class to handle group-level logic, allowing for "
"both function-based and class-based behaviors."
msgstr "集成 `GroupBehavior` 类处理组级逻辑，支持基于函数和基于类的行为。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:154
msgid ""
"Add ORCA (Optimal Reciprocal Collision Avoidance) behavior support "
"implemented by `pyrvo` library, this behavior can be configured in the YAML "
"file."
msgstr "新增由 `pyrvo` 库实现的 ORCA（最优互惠碰撞避免）行为支持，可在 YAML 文件中配置。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:155
msgid ""
"Update `behavior_registry` to support registration of behavior classes and "
"group behavior classes using decorators (`@register_behavior_class`, "
"`@register_group_behavior_class`)."
msgstr ""
"更新 "
"`behavior_registry`，支持使用装饰器（`@register_behavior_class`、`@register_group_behavior_class`）注册行为类和组行为类。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:156
msgid ""
"Add `viewpoint` YAML parameter for rendering the plot with the viewpoint of "
"the object."
msgstr "新增 `viewpoint` YAML 参数，以物体视角渲染绘图。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:159
msgid "Support chinese version documentation."
msgstr "支持中文版文档。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:160
msgid ""
"Update documentation for `group_behavior` configuration, including ORCA "
"parameters."
msgstr "更新 `group_behavior` 配置文档，包含 ORCA 参数。"

